data.description: PLEASE SEE A2A REMARKS! Explore this exquisite residence tucked away in the highly sought-after Independence Village neighborhood, peacefully nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac lot. This 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence boasts a modernized kitchen, elegant hardwood floors, and rejuvenated bathrooms. The expansive 3 Season's Room not only expands your living space but also introduces a touch of sophistication. Additionally, a supplementary patio and a privacy fence collaborate to form an enticing and secluded outdoor haven. The above ground family/rec room offers a multitude of possibilities. This property is priced to sell & won't be available for long!
